{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_0175H34kGRRZ1KsjncXFbVoM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01G3vQSuJQStxvssgeYsL5bx","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"### 17-3-run-command-parallel-integration — create-story (2026-04-04T20:42)","new_string":"### 17-3-run-command-parallel-integration — dev-story (2026-04-04T20:55)\n\n- **Vitest mock pattern**: `vi.fn()` mocks cannot be used with `new` via `mockReturnValue`. Had to create actual ES classes in hoisted block that delegate to mutable factory functions. Non-obvious pattern.\n- **File length**: `run.ts` grew from 203 to 340 lines. Story notes NFR9 max 300 lines per file. Could extract parallel path to `run-parallel.ts`.\n- **No integration test with real LanePool/WorktreeManager**: All tests mock pool and worktree manager. Real end-to-end behavior not tested at this level.\n\n## Token Report\n- Total tool calls: 30\n- By tool: Bash: 8, Read: 10, Edit: 18, Grep: 2, Write: 1, Glob: 1\n- Largest Bash outputs: `npx tsc --noEmit` (~33 lines), `npx vitest run run-parallel.test.ts` (~40 lines), `npx vitest run` grep (~22 lines)\n- Files read: 10 unique, 11 total reads\n- Redundant operations: None significant\n\n---\n\n### 17-3-run-command-parallel-integration — create-story (2026-04-04T20:42)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1234,"cache_read_input_tokens":52786,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1234},"output_tokens":73,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1e0d780f-040f-4c10-b8e5-df49ae6fae2c","uuid":"beae44a4-e3ac-4cf7-ba2c-5f7d3ab3e2a2"}
